        THANK_YOU_THANK_YOU_IT_S_A_MIRACLE                                      = 7233,  -- Thank you! Thank you! It's a miracle that even one of these letters came back to us safely. I had almost given up on the thought of seeing these ever again!
        IT_S_ONLY_A_LITTLE_BUT_PLEASE_TAKE                                      = 7234,  -- It's only a little, but please take it as a reward. We'll make sure that this mail gets delivered to the right person this time. Don't you worry about that!
