        IT_WOULD_BE_NO_EXAGGERATION_TO_SAY_THAT                                 = 9909,  -- It would be no exaggeration to say that, to us, cinder is worth more than its weight in gold! Bring it to me or my colleagues--preferably in large quantities--and you're sure to be pleased at what we can offer you in return.
