        A_LIFE_WITHOUT_INTELLECTUAL_CURIOSITY_IS_A_LIFE                         = 9929,  -- A life without intellectual curiosity is a life hardly worth living. Should your eyes one day open to this truth, you are free to return.
        I_THOUGHT_YOU_D_NEVER_ASK_SYNERGY_IS                                    = 9930,  -- I thought you'd never ask! Synergy is both an art and a science: an evolution--nay, a revolution--in synthesis.
