        THAT_S_WHY_SMART_SYNERGISTS_SYNERGIZE_IN_NUMBERS                        = 9940,  -- That's why smart synergists synergize in numbers. Too many culinarians might spoil the broth, but when it comes to synergy, it's the more the merrier!
