        RESETTING_REWARDS_WILL_INCREASE_THE_NUMBER_OF_DEEDS                     = 10474,  -- Resetting rewards will increase the number of deeds required but will let you reobtain items you have previously received.
        YOU_ARE_ABLE_TO_RESET_YOUR_REWARDS_FOR                                  = 10475,  -- You are able to reset your rewards for # deed[/s].
        RESET_REWARDS_YES_RESET_NO                                              = 10476,  -- Reset rewards? Yes. (Reset ##) No.
        YOU_HAVE_NOT_YET_RECEIVED_SOME_REWARDS_RESETTING                        = 10477,  -- You have not yet received some rewards. Resetting means that you will be unable to obtain them. Are you sure?
        REALLY_RESET_REWARDS_YES_RESET_NO                                       = 10478,  -- Really reset rewards? Yes. (Reset ##) No.
        REWARDS_HAVE_BEEN_RESET                                                 = 10479,  -- Rewards have been reset.
        THOSE_IMPUDENT_FOOLS_FROM_THAT_JEUNOAN_INSTITUTE_AFTER                  = 10480,  -- Those impudent fools from that Jeunoan institute. After their years of research, I'd thought them more astute.
        TO_LET_THAT_ROGUE_AJIDO_MARUJIDO_IN_ON                                  = 10481,  -- To let that rogue Ajido-Marujido in on the game, While I sit here dethroned, maligned, and shamed!
        IF_AN_ADVENTURER_POSSESSING_PASSED_THROUGH_MY_DOMAIN                    = 10482,  -- If an adventurer possessing % passed through my domain, It would give me no greater pleasure than to make them writhe in pain.
        WELL_WELL_I_SEE_THAT_HAS_COME_TO                                        = 10483,  -- Well, well, I see that % has come to visit me. This is no pleasant surprise. My heart is filled with rage, not glee.
        YES_SINCE_YOU_RE_HERE_I_LL_SHARE                                        = 10484,  -- Yes, since you're here, I'll share with you my brilliance: I've a task here which will test your resilience.
        TOGETHER_WE_ARE_TO_UNDERTAKE_THE_RITUAL_KNOWN                           = 10485,  -- Together we are to undertake the ritual known as Extreme Trust. If the ceremony fails, you are less than a blade covered in rust.
        ATTEMPT_THE_RITUAL_YES_NO_EXTREME_TRUST                                 = 10486,  -- Attempt the ritual? Yes. No. Extreme Trust?
        HOWEVER_CALM_OF_TEMPERAMENT_AND_POISED_I_SEEM                           = 10487,  -- However calm of temperament and poised I seem to be, step out of line and I'll have adventurer fricassee.
        IF_I_WERE_IN_YOUR_SHOES_I_WOULDN                                        = 10488,  -- If I were in your shoes, I wouldn't worry about the details. Just keep your eye on the prize, and your train of thought on the right trail. Ohohohohohoho!
        NOW_THAT_S_THE_RESPONSE_ONE_OF_MY                                       = 10489,  -- Now that's the response one of my stature likes to hear. With someone as grand as me to guide you, there's surely naught to fear.
        HOWEVER_LET_ME_FIRST_PROVIDE_YOU_WITH_SEVERAL                           = 10490,  -- However, let me first provide you with several words of warning. If this fails, it's on your head--and you won't live to see the morning.
        ATTEMPT_THE_RITUAL_ANYWAY_Y_YES_I_M                                     = 10491,  -- Attempt the ritual anyway? Y-yes...? I'm out.
        THIS_QUAKING_AND_QUAVERING_OF_YOURS_IS_NOT                              = 10492,  -- This quaking and quavering of yours is not attractive whatsoever.
        FEAR_NOT_FOR_THERE_IS_A_METHOD_BEHIND                                   = 10493,  -- Fear not, for there is a method behind the madness of this endeavor.
        SURELY_YOU_REMEMBER_WHEN_OTHERS_USED_MY_RESPLENDENT                     = 10494,  -- Surely you remember when others used my resplendent name for despicable acts. And yet, people laid the blame at my feet, ignoring all the facts.
        AS_AN_ASIDE_ONE_OF_MY_JOURNEYS_OF                                       = 10495,  -- As an aside, one of my journeys of late took me to [//yet ]another world. Though far be it from me to mention what calamities may have occurred.
        THERE_I_DISCOVERED_SOMETHING_WONDERFUL_A_VAST_SUM                       = 10496,  -- There I discovered something wonderful--a vast sum of advanced erudition. The five ministries could work for millennia and still be no competition.
        THE_WORLD_THAT_WE_KNOW_IS_FAR_MORE                                      = 10497,  -- The world that we know is far more expansive than we thought. All our treks, travels, and tomes--have our experiences been for naught?
        THOUGH_THE_DISTANCE_AT_FIRST_SEEMS_UNCROSSABLE_WHEN                     = 10498,  -- Though the distance at first seems uncrossable, When the universe is your oyster, nothing is impossible.
        DO_YOU_GET_WHAT_I_AM_TRYING_TO                                          = 10499,  -- Do you get what I am trying to say? We can cross whole dimensions--not in centuries, but today.
        DO_YOU_UNDERSTAND_P_PROBABLY_WHAT_RE_YOU                                = 10500,  -- Do you understand? P-probably... What're you on about?
        THE_PANICKED_LOOK_IN_YOUR_EYES_TELLS_ME                                 = 10501,  -- The panicked look in your eyes tells me all I need to know. To look smarter than you are, you decided to go with the flow.
        YOU_KNOW_THE_OLD_SAYING_APPEARANCES_CAN_BE                              = 10502,  -- You know the old saying, appearances can be deceiving? In your case, it's false, for your denseness is so obvious it's grieving.
        TO_BE_FRANK_IT_MATTERS_LITTLE_WHETHER_OR                                = 10503,  -- To be frank, it matters little whether or not you understand. If separate worlds are connected, then so is the common man.
        AND_WHAT_S_MORE_THIS_DOES_NOT_STOP                                      = 10504,  -- And what's more, this does not stop at Galka, Mithra, or Hume. All life is intertwined, like threads of wool on a loom.
        WHEN_I_TOOK_THE_TIME_TO_CONSIDER_FURTHER                                = 10505,  -- When I took the time to consider further, it gave me pause. Could I not utilize this knowledge to further my own cause?
        FOR_EXAMPLE_WHAT_IF_SOMEONE_WERE_TO_THREATEN                            = 10506,  -- For example, what if someone were to threaten my place in history? I could extract their mortal fears and make them writhe in misery.
        BUT_WHILE_I_WAS_PONDERING_THIS_FANTASTIC_PIECE                          = 10507,  -- But while I was pondering this fantastic piece of news, The fools in Jeuno announced something similar, so I lose!
        THEIR_METHODS_ARE_DIFFERENT_TRUST_FRIENDSHIP_AND_LOVE                   = 10508,  -- Their methods are different: trust, friendship, and love. But the theory's the same--and it fits like a glove.
        CAN_YOU_BELIEVE_IT_THEY_STOLE_THE_TOPIC                                 = 10509,  -- Can you believe it? They stole the topic of my next dissertation! I've half a mind to make them the target of my next conflagration.
        IMAGINE_THE_NERVE_OF_THOSE_INVOLVED_IN_THE                              = 10510,  -- Imagine the nerve of those involved in the project! It was a major affront and a sign of total disrespect.
        THOSE_WANT_TO_BE_WIZARDS_DENIED_ME_MY                                   = 10511,  -- Those want-to-be wizards denied me my prize, When, in the grand scheme of things, they're disease-ridden flies.
        THEY_REFUSED_TO_PROVIDE_ME_WITH_THE_FRUITS                              = 10512,  -- They refused to provide me with the fruits of my labor. I swear they will suffer--and I'm not rattling my saber!
        WHEN_ALL_THIS_IS_OVER_I_WILL_HAVE                                       = 10513,  -- When all this is over, I will have been more than just cruel. Their leader shall cower before me! I pity the fool!
        YET_EVEN_THAT_I_AM_WILLING_TO_OVERLOOK                                  = 10514,  -- Yet even that I am willing to overlook. For I shall have my way, by hook or by crook.
        SO_INSTEAD_I_HAVE_CHOSEN_TO_DEVELOP_THE                                 = 10515,  -- So instead, I have chosen to develop the magic myself. Come, stand beside me. Leave your reservations on the shelf.
        YES_MY_FIRST_SUBJECT_SHALL_BE_YOU_THERE                                 = 10516,  -- Yes, %, my first subject shall be you. There are many more worthy, but I suppose you will do.
        I_COMMAND_YOU_TO_TAKE_A_DEEP_BREATH                                     = 10517,  -- I command you to take a deep breath and close your eyes. Whether you will survive the process, I can only surmise.
        OHOHO_HMM                                                               = 10518,  -- Ohoho...hmm?
        WELL_NOW_YOU_VE_REALLY_GOT_EGG_ON                                       = 10519,  -- Well, %, now you've really got egg on your face. This can't be my fault, so it's you who's misplaced.
        THERE_IS_BUT_ONE_THING_YOU_CAN_DO                                       = 10520,  -- There is but one thing you can do, and it comes as no surprise. Let the cold darkness take you, and face your own demise!
        OHOHOHO_I_MIGHT_BE_THE_HARSHEST_MISTRESS_IN                             = 10521,  -- Ohohoho! I might be the harshest mistress in all of Vana'diel, But I may yet forgive you, if at my feet you kneel.
        I_COULDN_T_BE_MORE_MAGNANIMOUS_CONSIDERING_WHAT                         = 10522,  -- I couldn't be more magnanimous, considering what you've done. After all, the way you nearly killed that Taru left you under the gun.
        WHAT_S_THIS_THEN_YOU_DARE_CLAIM_I                                       = 10523,  -- What's this, then? You dare claim I was the mastermind? That brazen arrogance of yours is wholly unrefined.
        YOUR_ACCUSATIONS_ARE_IRRELEVANT_YOUR_MIND_SHROUDED_WITH                 = 10524,  -- Your accusations are irrelevant, your mind shrouded with fog. So let me continue--this is my monologue.
        STILL_THE_WAY_YOU_VANQUISHED_THE_SHADOW_LORD                            = 10525,  -- Still, the way you vanquished the Shadow Lord left me impressed. You didn't give in to terror, you refused to acquiesce.
        YOU_WON_THE_THANKS_OF_THE_NATION_FOR                                    = 10526,  -- You won the thanks of the nation for saving the Star Sibyl. For once, I shall admit to your prowess sans quibble.
        IN_FACT_IF_I_DEIGNED_TO_ASSIGN_YOU                                      = 10527,  -- In fact, if I deigned to assign you a grade, It would be an A+, for you came up in spades.
        WHEN_YOU_BROUGHT_BACK_THAT_FOOL_PRISHE_I                                = 10528,  -- [I think back on/I also remember] when you brought back that fool, Prishe. I'd wager that girl cannot fathom the horrors she unleashed.
        I_CAN_STILL_HEAR_YORAN_ORAN_WAILING_IN                                  = 10529,  -- I can still hear Yoran-Oran wailing in despair. I swear, Dr. Shantotto, there's no illegitimate heir-ethy!
        BUT_LOOKING_BACK_NOW_IT_WAS_A_GOOD                                      = 10530,  -- But looking back now, it was a good deal of fun. So I shall forgive you. All people get one.
        THERE_WAS_THAT_INCIDENT_WITH_RAGNAROK_WHEN_IT                           = 10531,  -- [If I remember correctly/Next, of course], there was that incident with Ragnarok. When it came to shedding blood, you certainly did not balk.
        OH_YOU_SAY_THE_SECOND_COMING_FAILED_TO                                  = 10532,  -- Oh? You say the second coming failed to ring true? That's not the point. I'm sure you did all you could do.
        AS_FOR_ME_I_REVELED_IN_OUTRAGEOUS_MILITARY                              = 10533,  -- As for me, I reveled in outrageous military spending. It was all quite fun... <Cough> I mean, I'm still lamenting!
        STUNT_YOU_PULLED_AT_THE_CHOCOBO_RACES_OH                                = 10534,  -- [That/And that] stunt you pulled at the chocobo races! Oh, how I wanted to make you one of my test cases!
        AND_TRUST_ME_UNGRATEFUL_YOU_WEREN_T_THE                                 = 10535,  -- And trust me, ungrateful %, you weren't the only one. I should have made sure that Markovich nevermore saw the sun!
        CHALLENGE_ME_TO_COMBAT_THINKING_YOU_COULD_WIN                           = 10536,  -- [I cannot forget your impudence when you decided to/Not one to rest on your laurels, you also had the gall to] challenge me to combat, thinking you could win. I hope you enjoyed my dear puppet twin.
        BUT_I_D_LIKE_TO_THINK_YOU_LEARNED                                       = 10537,  -- But I'd like to think you learned something from my little lesson. Since you were a good pupil, I'll overlook your transgression.
        TO_HIS_CREDIT_KORU_MORU_TOLD_ME_TO                                      = 10538,  -- To his credit, Koru-Moru told me to attack with that doll. But on further introspection, I should have set it to maul.
        THE_RITUAL_HAS_FAILED_COULD_IT_BE_PERHAPS                               = 10539,  -- [And yet, here you stand, and/Yet despite all your efforts,] the ritual has failed. Could it be, perhaps, that you got scared and bailed?
        REMEMBER_THAT_TIME_WITH_YORAN_ORAN_AND_KORU                             = 10540,  -- Remember that time with Yoran-Oran and Koru-Moru? Oh, weren't we just the best of friends, through and through?
        I_GAVE_YOU_THAT_HAT_THOUGH_IT_WAS                                       = 10541,  -- I gave you that hat, though it was covered in grime. So if you want to repay the favor, now is the time!
