        SURELY_KUPIPI_HAS_BEEN_TAUGHT_A_VALUABLE_LESSON                         = 10983,  -- Surely Kupipi has been taught a valuable lesson. That will teach her to rely less on her rolanberry delicatessen.
        NEXT_TIME_HER_CHEEKS_ARE_AFLUSH_WITH_DELICIOUS                          = 10984,  -- Next time her cheeks are aflush with delicious fruit, I'll head to Heavens Tower and give her the boot.
        FOR_SHOULD_SHE_CHOOSE_TO_IGNORE_ME_TO                                   = 10985,  -- For should she choose to ignore me to pursue plant-based delights, she'll have no mouth left to speak with, for I'll set it alight.
        BUT_ADVENTURER_DON_T_YOU_AGREE_THAT_SOMETHING                           = 10986,  -- But, adventurer, don't you agree that something's gone very wrong? It seems like everyone in Heavens Tower is a touch too far gone.
        IT_WAS_AN_IMPORTANT_DAY_FOR_THE_PEOPLE                                  = 10987,  -- It was an important day for the people who were there. How could they forget the truth you laid bare?
        IT_CERTAINLY_DOES_GIVE_ONE_LIKE_ME_PAUSE                                = 10988,  -- It certainly does give one like me pause. It's not like they signed a non-disparagement clause.
        NO_THE_CAUSE_OF_THIS_IS_SOMETHING_FAR                                   = 10989,  -- No, the cause of this is something far more sinister. I would swear to it as a former minister.
        I_BELIEVE_THE_ONE_WHO_SHOULD_INVESTIGATE_IS                             = 10990,  -- I believe the one who should investigate is you. You have quite the knack for picking up clues.
        HOW_DO_YOU_RESPOND_WHO_ME_WHAT_SHOULD                                   = 10991,  -- How do you respond? Who? Me? What should I do? I think it's your fault.
        PLEASE_AT_LEAST_PRETEND_TO_PAY_ATTENTION_OR                             = 10992,  -- Please at least pretend to pay attention. Or I might perform experiments on you too heinous to mention.
        STOP_LOOKING_ASKANCE_AND_HEAD_TO_HEAVENS_TOWER                          = 10993,  -- Stop looking askance and head to Heavens Tower. Unless, of course, you enjoy making me glower.
        RETURN_TO_THE_SCENE_AND_LEARN_ALL_YOU                                   = 10994,  -- Return to the scene and learn all you can. Maybe we can figure out where the true culprit ran.
        THEY_SAY_THE_CRIMINAL_ALWAYS_RETURNS_TO_THE                             = 10995,  -- They say the criminal always returns to the scene of the crime. Now hurry up, before we run out of time.
        SO_ENOUGH_WITH_THE_DAWDLING_AND_HEAD_OVER                               = 10996,  -- So enough with the dawdling and head over there. You've a mystery to solve--after that, we'll be square.
        I_SENSE_A_FRIGHTFUL_DISTURBANCE_AT_THE_CENTER                           = 10997,  -- I sense a frightful disturbance at the center of all this. Surely, you too know that something's amiss.
        IF_WE_ARE_TO_CONFRONT_THE_EVIL_THAT                                     = 10998,  -- If we are to confront the evil that threatens us all, everyone must do their part--big or small.
        SO_FOCUS_ON_YOUR_TASK_AND_STOP_BLAMING                                  = 10999,  -- So focus on your task and stop blaming me. Unless, of course, you'd prefer to be cast out to sea.
        THERE_S_A_PRICE_TO_BE_PAID_IF                                           = 11000,  -- There's a price to be paid if we don't discover the truth. And if that price is your head, I shall offer it up forsooth.
        TO_HEAVENS_TOWER_YOU_GO_WITHOUT_FURTHER_DELAY                           = 11001,  -- To Heavens Tower you go without further delay. You'll find answers there, not tomorrow, but today.
        AND_TO_KUPIPI_I_BID_YOU_DELIVER_A                                       = 11002,  -- And to Kupipi I bid you deliver a word. I'd send a pigeon, but I trust you more than a bird.
