        INDEED_I_AM_STARTING_TO_SEE_YOU_IN                                      = 11010,  -- Indeed, I am starting to see you in a new light. You've discerned the identity behind the sinister force that gave us all such a fright.
        NOW_THEN_LET_S_GET_RIGHT_TO_IT                                          = 11011,  -- Now then, let's get right to it, shall we? We must know the true identity of this culprit, don't you agree?
        WHO_IS_THE_CULPRIT_WHAT_ARE_YOU_TALKING                                 = 11012,  -- Who is the culprit? What are you talking about? It's Uran-Mafran. It's the Maelstrom Mage, Garazu-Horeizu. It's Caboose.
        SURELY_YOU_REMEMBER_THE_INCIDENT_AT_HEAVENS_TOWER                       = 11013,  -- Surely, you remember the incident at Heavens Tower? Speak now, or you'll be forced to witness my true power!
